{"tid":1529471,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"今日開學，原諒我唔可以再發咁多夢。","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:43:38.000Z","uid":312893,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"86a2c8cd7baff361124eb99f4581920dae5722ac","tid":1529471,"uid":312893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"第一次出post 唔知開咩台 希望有人睇<br />\n<br />\n每次發夢，我都去得八八九九<br />\n大多數都企中前線 <br />\n幫吓手set rb、淋熄吓tg咁<br />\n<br />\n第一次出嚟係612<br />\n考完個試就仆出嚟金鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰陣已經清緊埋 放緊tg<br />\n當日，亦係我第一次感受到香港人嘅愛，香港人嘅團結。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我就好似重新認識咗香港人咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有時又好鬼抵死，玩laser都可以開心成晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時又好認真，諗點樣打贏場仗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n每日十點嘅窗邊鳩叫<br />\n令我更加愛香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自豪自己係一個香港人，有你地陪伴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我係香港人啊hi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我地有經歷過高低起伏<br />\n一齊訓唔著 一齊喊<br />\n就好似<span style=\"color: violet;\">難兄難弟</span>咁共同進退<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n開學了<br />\n我唔可以再每一次都出嚟發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n身邊老師都勸：讀好書先有更大能力改變香港<br />\n<br />\n我知，我真係知<br />\n但我更想同巴打絲打喺戰場並肩作戰。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只不過，學業同家人嘅壓力<br />\n令我唔能夠再出得咁密<br />\n或者喺平日出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相信好多中學生都會一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過，我地嘅心依然不變：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港，時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n香港人萬事小心。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb85113535b1